Zardus looks down at Mosquitor as he falls out of the vines, his eyes showing a bit of contempt.

"He was a Predacon back when I was still new on this planet. We're probably in the ship that he came to earth with. It was years ago, so the vegetation in this area has gotten to it."

He kicks Mosquitor's body, the eyes flickering a bit.
